snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Help Wanted - Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
The team at Steel Wool is proud to bring you the Nintendo Switch version of Five Nights at Freddy's: Help Wanted. Turn off the lights, fire up the game and see how long before you jump up from fright!

RELEASE 5/21/2020 - 9AM PST
